channel.title: My Mopar Client
channel.description: Well..I'm a neeb at this stuff..but when i run my moparscape client..it has a narly 5 second lag on it..when i tele on ANY server..i have to wait for abut 45 seconds before it actually loads..same with logging in. Try clicking another window..it takes almost 2 minutes to open..not sure why...only does it when Mopar is running. Anyone know why?

@Duhsmersh wrote:

you probably have many other programs and windows running, or online messengers like MSN and AIM, i suggest that you close all other windows and stop other things that might cause lag. also if that doesn’t help try clearing your cache.
